		</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\" colspan=\"3\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" width=\"12%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">施工单位</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"33%\" colspan=\"2\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"100%\" colspan=\"8\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:200%;font-family:楷体_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">长沙市水利水电工程质量监督站：<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">我单位已于<u><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u>年<u><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u>月<u><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u>日组织完成本分部工程验收，工程达到设计标准，档案资料<u><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u>（齐全；基本齐全），验收遗留问题<u><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u>（无；已落实处理方案），工程验收质量等级为<u><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></u>，现申请予以备案。<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:10pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:5pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:174pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">项目法人技术负责人：<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:174pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">项目法人：（公章）<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:312pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">年</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"100%\" colspan=\"8\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">备案资料目录：<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">、分部工程验收鉴定书；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">、分部工程质量评定表；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">、单元工程质量评定表；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">、重要隐蔽（关键部位）单元工程质量等级签证表；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">、工程质量检测报告。<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\">、施工质量缺陷备案表；<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" width=\"9%\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">备案<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-align:center;\" align=\"center\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">意见<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:windowtext 1pt solid;border-left:windowtext 1pt solid;border-top:windowtext 1pt solid;border-right:windowtext 1pt solid;\" valign=\"top\" width=\"90%\" colspan=\"7\">\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:24pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">本分部工程质量检验与评定资料基本齐全，工程验收质量结论明确。依据《水利工程建设项目验收管理规定》，同意按<u> <b><span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</span></span></b></u>工程进行备案。</span><span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;font-size:5pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:270pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">（公章）<span></span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p style=\"text-indent:252pt;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">年<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>月<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span>日</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;\"></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n